remarks: The cardinality of a set with two distinct elements.  (Contributed by Thierry Arnoux, 27-Aug-2019.)
statement:
nehash2.p $e |- ( ph -> P e. V ) $.
nehash2.a $e |- ( ph -> A e. P ) $.
nehash2.b $e |- ( ph -> B e. P ) $.
nehash2.1 $e |- ( ph -> A =/= B ) $.
nehash2 $p |- ( ph -> 2 <_ ( # ` P ) ) $.
